summary: Hey gang! ✨ so I just launched a Patreon page I’m testing to see if this could help me with making more comics both original and...
caption:
Hey gang! ✨ so I just launched a Patreon page I’m testing to see if this could help me with making more comics both original and fanart. 

For now I can only share my wips, art process and early access posts, I will be talking more of other stuffs I can share with patreons only once I learn how to use this correctly 😂

So don’t feel pressure to become a patreon but if you still want to support, please help me with reblogs! Thank you 💖
